              <tr><td colspan="3">  <table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr><td width="200" valign="top"><b>Midnight Sea Mail Sleeves</b><br>
MAGIC ITEM &nbsp;LORE ITEM &nbsp;NO DROP &nbsp;<br>
AC: 8<br>
+1 STA, +20 MANA, +3 CR, +3 MR<br>
WT: 3.4 &nbsp;Size: ?<br>
Class: CLR, PAL<br>
Race: ERU</td>

  <td width="100" align="center" valign="top">
  <b>Item Icon</b><br>
  None Available</td>

  <td width="160" valign="top">
  <b>Obtained From</b><br>¤ Quest (15)<br>
</td>
  <td width="140" valign="top">
  <b>Additional Info</b><br>
  Type: Armor, Arms<br>
AC Per Stone: 2.35<br>
Date Added: 04/13/01<br>
<img src="images/print_w.gif" width="17" height="17" align="left"> <a href="itemsheet.php3?id=4707" target="_blank">Printable Version</a></td></tr>
