  <br><br>
  <b>Description</b><br>
Talk to Gans Paust and ask him "what of your brother?"  He will ask you if you could check on him.  He will hand you a note
and tell you to take it to Yelesom who can be found in Erudin.
<br><br>
Head off to Erudin and hand Yelesom the note.  He will tell you that his progress has been halted due to the fact that some furballs have stolen his tools.  He will ask you for help as well.  He will tell you that the beast that stole his toolkit and rowed out to the next island.  The first item you can recover is the Magnifying Glass, which is sitting on the gound [-600, 2000].  The hammer is sitting on the ocean floor right by the wall [-526, 2287].   To obtain the Toolkit, you will need to kill the Frantic Kerran who is still sitting in his boat.  Now put the Magnifying Glass and Hammer in the toolkit and hit combine.  Return to Yelesom with the toolkit and hand it to him. He will reward you with a letter.   Run back to Gans and he'll reward you with the Midnight Sea Mail Sleeves.</td></tr>
